ConformanceStatement.EnglishDescription: An instance of MSH.21 (Message Profile Identifier) SHALL contain the constant value 'PH_SS-Ack^SS Sender^2.16.840.1.114222.4.10.3^ISO' OR 'PH_SS-NoAck^SS Sender^2.16.840.1.114222.4.10.3^ISO'
MSH.1 (Field Separator) SHALL contain the constant value '|'.
MSH.2 (Encoding Characters) SHALL contain the constant value '^~\&'.
MSH-7 (Date/Time of Message) SHALL be expressed with a minimum precision of the nearest minute, and be represented in the following format: 'YYYYMMDDHHMM[SS[.S[S[S[S]]]]] [+/-ZZZZ]'.
MSH-9 (Message Type) SHALL be 'ADT^A08^ADT_A01'.
MSH-11 (Processing ID) SHALL have a value in the set of literal values ('P', 'D', 'T').
MSH-12 (Version ID) SHALL have the Literal Value of '2.5.1'.
